Allen A. Spizzo, MBA

Age : 59Linked companies :  Ferro Corporation 





Summary 



Mr. Allen A. Spizzo is a Member at United States Advanced Ceramics Association.He is on the Board of Directors at Ferro Corp. Mr. Spizzo was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Group Vice President by Metton America, Inc. and Chief Financial Officer & Vice President by Hercules, Inc.He also served on the board at OM Group, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from North Carolina State University and an MBA from the University of Akron.



