Why trust carrying your valuable rifle or shotgun with a poor quality sling, or even worse, none at all? Allen slings let you comfortably carry your firearm in style, and after over 40 years building firearm products and accessories, Allen has the right high quality carrying solution for your gun. Whether you're in the market for leather, nylon, neoprene, or rubber sling, Allen has slings that will not only look great but will serve you well for many years. Check out what OpticsPlanet has to offer in hunting slings, tactical slings, or sport shooting slings, and get FREE SHIPPING on all orders over $49!














